    <item>
      <title>Rivian 大幅削减生产目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-04/rivian-slashes-production-targets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五上午，电动汽车制造商 Rivian 股价暴跌，原因是该公司下调了年度生产目标，理由是其唯一一家美国组装厂的供应紧缩状况恶化。彭博社的 Ed Ludlow 加入了“彭博未平仓合约”，并详细介绍了情况。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-04/rivian-slashes-production-targets</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 15:31:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拉里·萨默斯称 9 月份降息 50 个基点是“一个错误”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/summers-says-50-basis-point-cut-in-september-was-a-mistake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前财政部长拉里·萨默斯表示，美联储上个月降息的决定是一个错误，因为新数据显示美国上个月的就业增长超过了所有预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/summers-says-50-basis-point-cut-in-september-was-a-mistake</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 15:28:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根大通和美国银行预计美联储 11 月不会降息半个百分点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/jpmorgan-bofa-no-longer-see-a-half-point-fed-cut-in-november</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通和美国银行目前预测，美联储将在 11 月份召开下次会议时将利率下调四分之一个百分点，在劳动力市场数据显示美国经济具有韧性之后，它们放弃了大幅降息的呼吁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/jpmorgan-bofa-no-longer-see-a-half-point-fed-cut-in-november</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 15:26:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国 Autodoc 邀请银行参与新一轮 IPO 计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/germany-s-autodoc-said-to-ask-banks-to-pitch-in-fresh-ipo-effort</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，德国在线汽车零部件经销商 Autodoc 已邀请银行参与其在法兰克福的潜在首次公开募股 (IPO)，这距离该公司上一次上市尝试大约三年。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/germany-s-autodoc-said-to-ask-banks-to-pitch-in-fresh-ipo-effort</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 15:25:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储官员古尔斯比谈“极佳”就业报告、通胀和利率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-04/fed-s-goolsbee-on-superb-jobs-report-inflation-rates-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[芝加哥联邦储备银行行长奥斯坦·古尔斯比 (Austan Goolsbee) 对 9 月份美国就业报告表示赞赏。古尔斯比在接受“彭博未平仓合约”节目 Mike McKee 采访时补充说，通胀率可能低于央行 2% 的目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-04/fed-s-goolsbee-on-superb-jobs-report-inflation-rates-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 14:45:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃里安在就业数据公布后警告美联储：“通胀尚未消退”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/el-erian-warns-fed-after-jobs-data-inflation-is-not-dead</link>
      <description><![CDATA[穆罕默德·埃利安表示，9 月份意外火爆的就业报告提醒人们“通货膨胀尚未消失”，美联储需要重新将重点放在抑制物价上涨上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/el-erian-warns-fed-after-jobs-data-inflation-is-not-dead</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 13:46:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>就业数据对债券市场造成冲击，交易员撤出对美联储大幅降息的押注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/traders-wipe-out-bets-on-big-fed-cuts-as-jobs-data-hits-bonds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国九月份就业数据超出预期并预示着强劲的招聘趋势后，交易员大幅削减了对美联储未来降息步伐的押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/traders-wipe-out-bets-on-big-fed-cuts-as-jobs-data-hits-bonds</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 12:49:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国就业报告缓解经济增长担忧，欧洲股市上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/european-stocks-edge-higher-as-investors-await-us-job-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲股市周五上涨，此前一份意外强劲的美国就业报告鼓舞了投资者，使他们相信经济状况良好。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/european-stocks-edge-higher-as-investors-await-us-job-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 07:16:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>精神航空努力达成救助协议以避免破产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/spirit-airlines-creditors-struggle-to-reach-rescue-debt-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，精神航空重组债务、避免申请破产的努力遭遇阻碍，因为经过数月与债券持有人的谈判，该公司未能达成协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/spirit-airlines-creditors-struggle-to-reach-rescue-debt-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 00:41:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员重新思考美联储路径，股市和收益率上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国股市小幅上涨，此前就业报告强于预期，凸显了经济实力，并提振了软着陆的希望。该数据削弱了人们对美联储下个月再次大幅降息的预期，导致美国国债遭到抛售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 22:27:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
